ca.uhn.hl7v2.protocol

Class ReceivingApplicationException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • ca.uhn.hl7v2.protocol.ReceivingApplicationException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class ReceivingApplicationException
extends Exception
    Represents any problem encountered during processing of a message by a ReceivingApplication. Note that this replaces ca.uhn.hl7v2.app.ApplicationException in HAPI 0.5.
